name: Quality Amytlo Executioner
raw:
<font color=#009B00>

This Instruction Manual will teach you how to assemble a:
 'Quality Amytlo Executioner'
The Construction kit. must be between Quality Level 81 and 120.
All other pieces must be of AT LEAST that level range... 
Add them using shift+right-click.
Add the pieces in the following order:

 1. One Handed Edged Weapons Construction kit.

 2. Notum Enriched Nano Paste - 2x Layer. . SkillTo Assemble: Nano Progra: 162-240

 3. Medium Handle. . SkillTo Assemble: Weapon Smt: 298-441

 4. Notum Enriched Nano Paste - 1x Layer. . SkillTo Assemble: Nano Progra: 122-180

 5. Optimized Co-Weapon Interface. . SkillTo Assemble: Comp. Liter: 243-360
